2.0.0 (2015-04-23)
==================

**Breaking changes**

- Remove trailing slash from API URLs (/api/models.json instead of /api/models/)

**Bug fixes**

- Fix LastModifiedMixin to handle all dispatch() parameters


1.16.0 (2015-03-20)
